summary:
• Over 4 years of experience as a diligent Project Management Officer offering a proven record of success supporting all phases of diverse projects (It, e-Commerce, SaaS) within constraints (schedule, functionality, budget) 

• Excellent communicator; leverage technical, business and financial acumen to communicate effectively with Project Managers and their respective teams

• Business strategist; planning, implementing and optimizing project and control functions aligning business goals with technology solutions to drive process improvements, competitive advantage and bottom-line gains

• Expert in Agile project management methodologies. Known for ability to support in producing high-quality deliverables

• Hands on, patient and diligent, quality focused, keen learner.
